title: Real Humans S1 Ep3
description:
Real Humans S1 Ep3

The Lord shall be Our Companion - In a parallel present day, robots have become so human it is barely possible to distinguish them from real people. In this episode, the rogue hubots take refuge in an old church, where the pastor offers them sanctuary in the vicarage, believing that hubots would never harm humans. Granddad Lennart has trouble accepting his new housekeeper and takes every chance he can get to get away from her and enjoy the freedom he once had with Odi. Stars Andreas Wilson, Lisette Pagler and Pia Halvorsen. 

From Sweden, in Swedish

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
